title: Can't see my own club
body: I'm club owner, and can't see it. It's been an issue for a while now. Please advise.

replies.body: Should be fixed now, can you try accessing your club again and let us know if you have access?

Welcomed.

Special thanks to my  partners in crime, Broporo & Prynce! (They did everything tbh)

1. How long has this been an issue? 
2. Do you experience connectivity issues with the client or in-game?
